I hope my mom is hearing these from the above❤️
1) She was an Iron Lady 
2) Loves her children unconditionally 
3) Never spend her money for herself
4) Always saying sorry to her children even if she was right
5) Every step that she makes,her children was in her mind
6) She doesn't expects gifts from her children but instead shower them with it
7) She didn’t earn big bucks but she will always use her magic hands to Ensure we have 3 proper meals
8) She doesn't spend time with friends because her children were her friends
9) She never make her children feel that they were lousy and ungrateful.She always understand them by thinking that they were busy and had their own life
10) Lastly she was always proud of all of us and never said that her kids didn't do this or that *What an amazing lady she is😘I often ask myself if I could be as amazing as she was🤔May we reunite in Jannah❤️Aamiin
